{
  "texts": [
    "Challenges in knowledge graph question answering 1.",
    "Semantic fidelity in query translation: A critical challenge in LLM-powered KGQA systems is semantic drift during natural language-to-KG-query conversion (Li H. et al., 2024).",
    "Current LLM-driven retrieval-enhanced methods [such as ChatKBQA (Luo H. et al., 2023) ] face semantic fidelity issues when dealing with complex queries.",
    "When handling queries with implicit constraints, LLM-generated queries often lose critical elements such as temporal ranges or comparative logic.",
    "While GoG (Xu et al., 2024) partially mitigates this issue through a generate-retrieve framework, semantic deviations in the generation phase directly lead to retrieval results deviating from user intent."
  ]
}